cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.ST

The paper discusses a machine learning approach for improving the robustness of logistic regression, which is a fundamental method in classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of ITL for robust machine learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as well. The experiments involve toy examples and public datasets, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method compared to existing methods, which could be considered as a statistical analysis and thus belong to cs.ST (Statistics).
